channel.title: [PI] Engine Load problem
channel.description: I am using Marcbobs source, and i have an engine load problem, with 7 players is is up to 31%, when it used to be around 1% per person, I just fixed up chaotic maul, and added some new commands, what could be causing this?

item.title: [PI] Engine Load problem
item.dc:creator: @deathe1000 deathe1000
item.description:
@deathe1000 wrote:

[quote=“AtomicInt_, post:4, topic:445022”]It’s not your anti virus software.

Don’t listen to the engine load in the Command Prompt, it’s horribly written and inaccurate.

But it is most likely memory leaks. Project Insanity is full of them.[/quote]

Oh ok, thanks bro
